    "title": "How to turn your OpenClaw into the world's best assistant",
    "preview_text": "I turned my @openclaw into the most effective assistant and chief of staff I’ve ever worked with.\n\nI’ve hired executive assistants in previous companies, and I’m honestly blown away by how well this",
