            {
              "length": 18,
              "offset": 60,
              "style": "Italic"
            }
          ],
          "key": "cd9v1",
          "text": "A lot of the ideas for the priority map, auto-resolver, and ingestion pipeline were inspired by @pedroh96 OpenClaw setup, which he talked about on Core Memory with @ashleevance at youtube.com/watch?v=9ZbbxSgrjhw&t=3847s",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
