          "text": "your tolerance for interruptions",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "fehp",
          "text": "The more you customize it, the more valuable it becomes.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "eq8a9",
          "text": "Generic assistants are generic because they are under-configured.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "fe6cb",
          "text": "Great assistants are opinionated, specific, and deeply shaped around one person’s operating reality.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8i8dg",
          "text": "Final thought",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "bhfkn",
          "text": "I didn’t get the world’s best assistant by asking OpenClaw better questions.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3prdk",
          "text": "I got it by giving OpenClaw a better operating system.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9ulh9",
          "text": "That’s what clawchief is.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "enae2",
          "text": "If you want the shortcut, start here:",
